712359f-b.text:
(1)
St. Clare Parochial School (the new building), 423-425 West 36th Street, north side, between Ninth and Tenth Avenues.
July 21, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.

(2)
The same, a year later, seen from the clearing for the avenue which is to lead traffic to the midtown tunnel. The school lies directly in the way, and is being demolished.
March 18, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.

(3)
The same, seven and a half years earlier, showing some of the children.
October 6, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
